            <title>[PDFBOX-2939] PDFRenderer.renderImageWithDPI exception with certain PDFs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2939</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I use the PDFRender in my application and noticed that the renderImageWithDPI method throws an exception with certain pdf files. The bug can be reproduced with the pdfbox-app  command below. The medibank.pdf file is available via my Google Drive account:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7b7_UXpgIdGb2djYTNDNmVtVTA/view?usp=sharing&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7b7_UXpgIdGb2djYTNDNmVtVTA/view?usp=sharing&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ java -jar pdfbox-app-2.0.0-20150819.113526-1604.jar PDFToImage medibank.pdf&lt;br/&gt;
